description:
**Somalia: 112,448 displacements, 01 June - 30 June**    
 According to OCHA and the Protection and Return Monitoring Network (PRMN), 112,448 people were displaced by drought in the month of June. This represents a 231 % increase from the number recorded in May.   
 [Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs (OCHA) - 13 July 2022](https://reliefweb.int/report/somalia/drought-displacement-monitoring-dashboard-june-2022)
